Description.SourceString: An inventive and volatile engineer, Caleb derived all his passion from his groundbreaking designs. When a wealthy man stole his life's work, revenge became his sole priority.
A fitted, long-sleeved coat to keep his weapons and devices concealed but easy to reach.
A sharp weapon with a strong bite.
An inventive and volatile engineer, Caleb derived all his passion from his groundbreaking designs. When a wealthy man stole his life's work, he sought to tear his body apart limb from limb.
A fitted, long-sleeved coat to keep his targets from drenching his weapons and devices in blood.
A sharp weapon with a strong bite... and a thirst for blood.
A daring, modern, workaholic filmmaker, Zarina strove to reveal hidden truths.
A loose jacket to conceal the recording devices she brings for improvised recordings and interviews.
Flexible denim pants to venture the streets of Brooklyn and brave any type of weather.
A daring, modern, workaholic filmmaker, Zarina strove to share truths written in blood.
A loose jacket to conceal the blood smeared equipment she carries.
Flexible denim pants to venture Brooklyn and brave any type of trouble.
A weathered leather jacket to conceal the clunky recording devices she carries for impromptu interviews.
